### List all lessons
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lessons

### Filter by style
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lessons?style=HIPHOP

### Filter by difficulty
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lessons?difficulty=BEGINNER

### Filter by both
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lessons?style=HIPHOP&difficulty=BEGINNER

### Get one lesson by id (replace with a real UUID from your DB)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa

### Try invalid id (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000